law.text:
This subtitle does not apply to:
An insurance company subject to the provisions of the Insurance Article;
A railroad operating in this State;
A national bank that:
Has its main office located in this State; or
Does not maintain a branch in this State;
A federal credit union; or
A foreign nonstock corporation whose only activity in this State is supplying police, fire, rescue, or emergency services personnel on a nonprofit basis to assist in an area covered by a state of emergency declared by the Governor under § 14-107 of the Public Safety Article.
